    Github: https://github.com/creativeplatform

5. What do you plan to build with Envio's indexing capabilities? Please include a **motivation for your grant application.** *We might ask to have a quick 15-min call if there are any parts of the application that seems unclear.*

    **Real-Time NFT Listings:** Use Envio to index NFT listings in real-time. When artists and creators list their NFTs on your platform, these listings should be instantly available to users, ensuring that they have the most up-to-date information about available NFTs.

    **Real-Time Price Tracking:** Provide users with real-time price tracking for NFTs. They should be able to see the current price of an NFT as well as any price changes as they occur.

    **Interactive NFT Explorer:** Develop an interactive NFT explorer that allows users to search and filter NFTs based on various criteria, and see the results update in real-time as they apply filters.

    **Security and Trust:** Ensure that all real-time data indexed by Envio is accurate and secure, building trust among users that the information they see on your platform is reliable.

